CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 15, 1970, pg. 22 reads: "These Young Lovelies were fashionably mod as they "did their thing" in "Soul Dressings '70" Fashion show.... Second photo, same order: Marleen Smith, Tracey Marsh, Yvonne Barksdale and Vonnie Hill. -Harris photos."
TitMainTitle: Marleen Smith, Tracey Marsh, Yvonne Barksdale, and Vonnie Hill, modeling clothing during the "Soul Dressings '70" fashion show
